title: EViews 10.0 Enterprise Incl Patch
description:
Description: 
EViews 10.0 Enterprise от Сентябрь 19 2017 + x64 Econometric package Eviews provides a particularly complex and delicate data processing tools, allows you to perform regression analysis, build forecasts in a Windows-centric computer environment. With the help of this software, you can very quickly identify the presence of statistical dependence in the analyzed data and then, using the obtained relationships, to make a forecast of the studied indicators. 
It is advisable to distinguish the following spheres of Eviews application: 
1. analysis of scientific information and evaluation; 
2. financial analysis; 
3. macroeconomic forecasting; 
4. Simulation; 
5. forecasting the state of markets. 
Especially wide opportunities are opened by Eviews when analyzing data presented in the form of time series. 

Developer: Quantitative Micro Software 
License: ShareWare - for you free of charge 
Language: English - Russian version and Russifier not available 
Size: 73 + 76 MB 
OS: Windows
